Introduction

HITGS is a girl group under H Music Entertainment. The group name is an abbrevation for "Hip, Innocent, Teenager, Girls, Story". They made their official debut on April 28, 2025, with the Single Album, "Things we love : H", and it's title track "Sourpatch".

Originally formed under the name Project H, the group had been a hot topic even before their official debut. They performanced at the pre-show of '2024 SBS Gayo Daejeon', and attended the 'TIRTIR' pop-up store opening event and '2025 F/W Seoul Fashion Week'.
